OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FQuite cloudy to start on
OL,6,FSaturday with some rain in the west,
OL,7,Fsleety on high ground, cloud clearing
OL,8,Fin the afternoon with some bright
OL,9,Fconditions for most places, mainly
OL,10,Flight winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClouding over in the evening
OL,13,Fwith some rain spreading east and
OL,14,Ffreshening southwesterly winds, drier
OL,15,Ffor a time but further rain by dawn.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA wet and windy start in the
OL,18,Fwest on Sunday rain quite persistent
OL,19,Ffor Dumfries and Galloway but brighter
OL,20,Fin the east with more intermittent
OL,21,Frain, quite blustery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
